            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We do not include any harmful parabens or other nasties. We also NEVER test on animals.</p><ul><li><strong>Hyaluronic Acid - </strong>It deeply hydrates and plumps the skin, helping reduce fine lines and giving a smooth, dewy glow overnight.<br/></li><li><strong>Niacinamide - </strong>It helps brighten skin tone, smooth texture, and strengthen the skin barrier while calming redness and minimizing pores.<br/></li><li><strong>Glycerin - </strong>It draws moisture into the skin, keeping it soft, smooth, and hydrated throughout the night.<br/></li><li><strong>Ceramide Np - </strong>It helps strengthen the skin barrier, lock in moisture, and protect against dryness and irritation<br/></li></ul><p>As with all skincare products, we highly recommend & urge you please patch test the mask serum on the skin of the arm or hand before using fully as some people are more sensitive than others or have allergic reactions to blends of ingredients.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Key Benefits",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Turn Back Time on Wrinkles: </strong>Smooth fine lines and improve skin elasticity while you sleep—wake up to firmer, younger-looking skin without the effort.</p><p><strong>Glow That Gets Noticed: </strong>Infused with niacinamide and collagen to revive dull, tired skin and give you that fresh, radiant “glass skin” glow.</p><p><strong>Simple to Use, No-Stress Routine: </strong>Just apply before bed, let it dry into a breathable film, and peel off in the morning—no sticky mess, just results.</p><p><strong>Powerhouse Ingredients, Gentle Formula: </strong>Formulated with collagen, hyaluronic acid, ceramides, and adenosine—no harsh additives, just skin-loving nourishment.</p><p><strong>All-in-One Overnight Repair: </strong>Hydrates, plumps, smooths texture, and strengthens your skin barrier—perfect for dry, aging, or stressed-out skin.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_8h6X4m": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Should I wash after the mask?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>No, it is not necessary to wash your face after use. The remaining serum can be gently massaged into the skin for extra hydration.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_WYG8GJ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it for sensitive skin?",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes! Designed to be gentle on the skin. Our mask does not strip moisture or dry out, making it ideal for all skin types.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 0,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QGc8Kr": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping & Returns",
            "heading_size": "small",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Processing Time:</strong><br/>Once your order is placed, please allow 24 hours for us to process and prepare your order for shipment.<br/><br/><strong>Shipping Time:</strong><br/>After your order is dispatched, it will typically take 4-8 business days to reach you, depending on your location.<br/><br/><strong>Tracking Information:</strong><br/>Once your order has been shipped, you will receive an email containing your tracking number. You can use this to track your package and stay updated on its delivery status.</p><p><strong>Returns:<br/></strong>We want you to be fully satisfied with your purchase! If you are not completely happy with your order, we accept returns and exchanges within 60 days from the date of purchase.<br/><br/>Contact us via the website or via email: info@niforashop.com</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
