    "ss_product_ingredients_6_drFDty": {
      "type": "ss-product-ingredients-6",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_UTTTmp": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<p><strong>Every Ingredient Carefully Chosen</strong></p>",
            "heading_custom": false,
            "heading_font": "poppins_n7",
            "heading_size": 36,
            "heading_size_mobile": 32,
            "heading_height": 130,
            "heading_mt": 0,
            "heading_mt_mobile": 0,
            "heading_color": "#8b1638"
          }
        },
        "text_Hpq9BG": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Each ingredient in our <strong>Collagen Wrapping Mask</strong> is meticulously selected and supported by science — not hype. We steer clear of harsh fillers and hidden additives to deliver a clean, effective formula infused with clinically backed actives like <strong>collagen peptides</strong>, <strong>niacinamide</strong>, <strong>hyaluronic acid</strong>, and <strong>ceramide NP</strong>,  all working together to deeply hydrate, visibly firm, and smooth mature or dehydrated skin. Because real results start with real ingredients.<br/><br/></p>",
            "text_custom": false,
            "text_font": "josefin_sans_n4",
            "text_size": 13,
            "text_size_mobile": 13,
            "text_height": 130,
            "text_mt": 4,
            "text_mt_mobile": 12,
            "text_color": "#121212"
          }
        },
        "card_VfrHqA": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Niacinamide_78c86079-2000-4e45-a05f-61a2ff51585a.png",
            "title": "Niacinamide",
            "text": "<p>Brightening support</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p>Our <strong>Collagen Wrapping Mask</strong> is enriched with <strong>Niacinamide</strong> — a multitasking form of vitamin B3 known for its brightening and skin-refining properties. It helps to <strong>even out skin tone</strong>, reduce the appearance of <strong>enlarged pores</strong>, and <strong>smooth rough texture</strong>. Niacinamide also supports the skin barrier and soothes irritation, making it ideal for restoring clarity, resilience, and balance to tired or uneven skin.</p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_xCFN9d": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Hyaluronix.png",
            "title": "Hyaluronic Acid",
            "text": "<p>Boosts Skin Hydration</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p><strong>Hyaluronic acid </strong>is a moisture-binding ingredient that <strong>deeply hydrates the skin</strong>, helping it appear plump, smooth, and supple. It holds up to 1,000 times its weight in water,<strong> supporting skin elasticity</strong> and <strong>reducing the look of fine lines</strong>. In the Bio-Collagen Mask, it enhances absorption and boosts the mask’s firming and rejuvenating effects.</p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_XMQ4Hc": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Glycerin_1.png",
            "title": "Glycerin",
            "text": "<p>Deep hydration</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p><strong>Glycerin</strong> — a powerful humectant known for its ability to attract and retain moisture deep within the skin. It helps to <strong>hydrate, soften, and smooth</strong> the complexion by reinforcing the skin’s natural moisture barrier. Glycerin also enhances the mask’s overall absorption, ensuring that every active ingredient penetrates effectively—leaving the skin feeling <strong>plump, dewy, and refreshed</strong>.</p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_xMQVgi": {
          "type": "card",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Ceramide.png",
            "title": "Ceramide",
            "text": "<p>Barrier repair</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p>Our <strong>Collagen Wrapping Mask</strong> is formulated with <strong>Ceramide NP</strong> — a skin-identical lipid that plays a key role in maintaining a <strong>strong, healthy skin barrier</strong>. It helps to <strong>lock in moisture</strong>, protect against environmental stressors, and <strong>prevent transepidermal water loss</strong>. By reinforcing the skin’s natural defenses, Ceramide NP supports long-lasting hydration, improves resilience, and leaves the skin feeling <strong>smooth, calm, and well-nourished</strong></p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_tp48nh": {
          "type": "card",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Glycerin.png",
            "title": "Glycerin",
            "text": "<p>Moisture Lock</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p><strong>Glycerin </strong>is a powerful humectant that draws moisture into the skin and <strong>helps maintain hydration levels</strong>. It works to soften rough patches, improve skin elasticity, and support the skin’s natural barrier. In the Bio-Collagen Mask, it helps lock in moisture,<strong> keeping the skin plump</strong>, smooth, and comfortable during and after use.</p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_PhU7dr": {
          "type": "card",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Galactomyces.png",
            "title": "Galactomyces",
            "text": "<p>Radiance Booster</p>",
            "source": "",
            "modal_text": "<p><strong>Galactomyces</strong> is a fermented yeast extract rich in vitamins, amino acids, and antioxidants that <strong>help nourish and revitalize the skin</strong>. It works to improve skin clarity, <strong>refine pores</strong>, and balance sebum production. It <strong>enhances radiance</strong>, <strong>smooths texture</strong>, and supports a brighter, more even complexion.<br/></p>",
            "modal_subtitle": "",
            "modal_sub_text": "",
            "url": ""
          }
        },
        "card_QBr6FW": {
          "type": "card",
